<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Crear escena</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-4bw+/aepP/YC94hEpVNVgiZdgIC5+VKNBQNGCHeKRQN+PtmoHDEXuppvnDJzQIu9" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a80e1d56f1.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('navbar') %>
   

    <main class="container-fluid">
      <section class="row sctform">
        <div class="col-12 text-center rotulo">
          <p>(Crea una escena)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-xl-6 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-5">
          <div class="txt1 text-white text-center rounded-3 p-3">
            <p>En esta ubicación se grabó una escena mitica y aun no la han creado, y tu, lo sabes. ¡Asi que no esperes mas y crea una nueva escena rodadad en este emblematico lugar!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-xl-6 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="contform">
            <form class="formulario d-flex flex-column gap-2"
            action="/sequence/createSequence/<%= messageId %>"
            method="post"
            enctype="multipart/form-data">    
              <input type="text"          
                    name="movie"
                    placeholder="Pelicula"/>    
              <input type="text"          
                    name="year"
                    placeholder="Año"/>
              <textarea  name="synopsis"  
                        rows="3" 
                        minlength="1" 
                        maxlength="280" 
                        placeholder="Resumen"></textarea>
              <input type="file"
                    name="img">  
              <button type="submit" class="btn css-button-arrow--red">Crear</button>    
              <h5 class="text-danger"><%= typeof message != 'undefined' ? message : null %></h5>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>        
      </section>
    </main>


    <%- include('footer') %>